HexaBus - The Kraken of Home Automation

Visit hexabus.net and release the Kraken!


This repository contains the firmware for the Hexabus hardware as well as the host software we're working on. Go to signup.hexabus.net to find out how to get your own Hexabus starter kit and start hacking. If you want to get in touch with us directly, you can visit #hexabus on irc.hackint.eu